            "description": "**Use Case**: Link Aster exchange credentials to user account.\n\n**Payload**:\n- `userId`: From Create User response\n- `exchange`: \"aster\"\n- `apiKey`: Aster API key\n- `apiSecret`: Aster API secret\n\n**Security**: Credentials are encrypted before storage."
