    {
      "name": "üîê Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Unified Session",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.success) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"authToken\", jsonData.token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"exchangeId\", jsonData.activeExchange);",
                  "    console.log(\"‚úÖ Unified session created\");",
                  "    console.log(\"Active Exchange: \" + jsonData.activeExchange);",
                  "    console.log(\"Linked Exchanges: \" + jsonData.linkedExchanges.join(', '));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"userId\": \"{{userId}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/session",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "session"]
            },
            "description": "**Use Case**: Create unified session that works with ALL linked exchanges.\n\n**New Behavior**: \n- Creates ONE session for all linked exchanges\n- No need to specify exchangeId (uses first linked exchange as default)\n- Switch exchanges using /auth/session/switch\n\n**Auto-Action**: Sets `authToken` and `exchangeId` variables.\n\n**Token Validity**: 24 hours\n\n**Response**: Returns active exchange and list of all linked exchanges"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Session Info ‚ú®",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/session/info",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "session", "info"]
            },
            "description": "**Use Case**: Get current session metadata.\n\n**Response**:\n- userId\n- activeExchange (currently selected exchange)\n- linkedExchanges (all available exchanges)\n- createdAt, expiresAt\n\n**When to use**: Check which exchange is currently active, see all linked exchanges"
          },
          "response": []
        },
